[en_US]
Enable test mode & Enhanced power

Hacker: HappyASR[EGCG] & Creamymami[EGCG]

Description:
- Press 'P1 Start' to enter test mode.
- Get power up on a valid attack or being attacked.
- Get scores at 4 times normal speed.


